  "title": "Sales Executive #81150",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Wholesaler</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Sales Executive</strong></li><li>Working Location: Mandai (Islandwide)</li><li>Working Hours: 6 days (Mon-Sat: 8.30am-6.30pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic up to $3,000 + Commission + Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Reach out to new and existing customers to share and promote our range of fruits and vegetables.</li><li>Build and maintain good long-term relationships with customers to support satisfaction and repeat orders.</li><li>Handle customer orders and work with the logistics team to arrange delivery.</li><li>Achieve sales targets through active selling and suggesting suitable add-on items when appropriate.</li><li>Stay updated on our products and general market trends so you can give useful recommendations.</li><li>Provide updates to the management team on sales results, customer feedback, and market observations.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Sales experience is preferred, but not required.</li><li>Good communication skills and the ability to build good working relationships with customers.</li><li>Driven to meet goals and enjoy working towards sales targets.</li><li>Able to work independently, stay organized, and manage your tasks well.</li><li>Able to work in a fast-paced environment and adjust to customers’ changing needs.</li><li>Basic computer skills (MS Office, CRM systems).</li><li>Class 3 driving license is an advantage.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#81150 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
